Class HerzliaWarehouse

  • java.lang.Object
    • creational.toys.warehouse.AbstractWarehouse
      • creational.toys.warehouse.herzlia.HerzliaWarehouse

  • public class HerzliaWarehouse
extends AbstractWarehouse
    Here I use a Bridge design pattern to sell a car Herzlia class is responsible for selling the car it have been created. Once the car is created we can sell it through the exporter class, and here comes the bridge design pattern to save us.
